      <title>DigitalX 将在澳大利亚主要股票市场上市比特币 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/digitalx-to-list-bitcoin-etf-on-australia-s-main-stock-market</link>
